import React from 'react' import '../index.css' export default function Project() { return ( <>

Projects

  • TextUtils

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Decscription: It offers features such as converting entered text into uppercase, lowercase letters, copying the text and also character/word count analysis.

  • Basic Landing Page of a Company

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs, API

    Decscription: It contains basic home -page, about-page and contact.

  • Registeration Form

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Decscription: s. It has input validations and on incorrect input, it shows alerts.

  • NewsMonkey

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs, API

    Decscription: s. It is a dynamic web application that harnesses the power of APIs to deliver real time news updates to users.

  • Calculator

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Decscription: It performs basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, division and also supports parantheses.

  • CountDown Timer

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Decscription: It has functionality of sta rting , stopping , restarting and resetting the timer.

  • Currency Converter

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Decscription: Through the integration of external currency exchange API, users can effortlessly convert USD to a range of other currencies.

  • Login Page

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Decscription: It implements input validation, error alerts and password hashing for enhanced security.

  • Notes

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Description: It has functionality of adding, deleting, editing a note and also keep history of notes.

  • Personal Portfolio

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs

    Decscription: s. It showcases my education, skills and contact information, presenting a overview of my professional profile.

  • AI-Image-Generator

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, API

    Decscription: n. It can generate images relevant to the entered text.

  • React-Dall-E-Clone

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs, API

    Decscription: It can create images relevant to the entered text and also generate variations of the selected image

  • JavaScript-ChatGpt-Clone

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, API

    Decscription: It is a dynamic conversational interface.

  • React-ChatGpt-Clone

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs, API

    Decscription: It is a dynamic conversational interface.

  • SQL-Generator

    Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJs, API

    Decscription: It has functionality of generating queries for entered text.
